{"id":"21043","name":"兩個人的演唱會","rarity":4,"path":"Knight","desc":"「哥哥，這是……」 \n「好久沒有快樂地唱過歌了吧…我為你搭了一座舞台，就是…有點簡陋。」 \n「但老師覺得我不適合……」 \n「不，我覺得很好聽！以後你一定會實現自己的夢想，站在更大的舞台上歌唱……」 \n……\n許多年之後，她站在璀璨的舞台上，望著底下洶湧的粉絲，卻失神了片刻——\n在漫長的追夢路上，她總會想起那道信任的目光，和自己的第一場「演唱會」。\n沒有絢麗的燈光，沒有華美的妝造，有的只是一個孩子為了鼓勵另一個孩子追求夢想而搭建起的舞台。\n「如今，我們的夢都實現了。但…那還是屬於『我們』的夢嗎……」 \n她握緊了話筒。在下一首歌開始之前，她甚至來不及感到悲傷。","icon":"icon/light_cone/21043.png","preview":"image/light_cone_preview/21043.png","portrait":"image/light_cone_portrait/21043.png","ranks":{"id":"21043","skill":"鼓舞","desc":"使裝備者的防禦力提高#1[i]%。場上每有一名持有護盾的角色，裝備者造成的傷害便提高#2[i]%。","params":[[0.16,0.04],[0.2,0.05],[0.24,0.06],[0.28,0.07],[0.32,0.08]],"properties":[[{"type":"DefenceAddedRatio","value":0.16}],[{"type":"DefenceAddedRatio","value":0.2}],[{"type":"DefenceAddedRatio","value":0.24}],[{"type":"DefenceAddedRatio","value":0.28}],[{"type":"DefenceAddedRatio","value":0.32}]]},"promotions":{"id":"21043","values":[{"hp":{"base":43.2,"step":6.48},"atk":{"base":16.8,"step":2.52},"def":{"base":21,"step":3.15}},{"hp":{"base":95.04,"step":6.48},"atk":{"base":36.96,"step":2.52},"def":{"base":46.2,"step":3.15}},{"hp":{"base":164.16,"step":6.48},"atk":{"base":63.84,"step":2.52},"def":{"base":79.8,"step":3.15}},{"hp":{"base":233.28,"step":6.48},"atk":{"base":90.72,"step":2.52},"def":{"base":113.4,"step":3.15}},{"hp":{"base":302.4,"step":6.48},"atk":{"base":117.6,"step":2.52},"def":{"base":147,"step":3.15}},{"hp":{"base":371.52,"step":6.48},"atk":{"base":144.48,"step":2.52},"def":{"base":180.6,"step":3.15}},{"hp":{"base":440.64,"step":6.48},"atk":{"base":171.36,"step":2.52},"def":{"base":214.2,"step":3.15}}],"materials":[[{"id":"2","num":4000},{"id":"114011","num":5}],[{"id":"2","num":8000},{"id":"110211","num":3},{"id":"114011","num":10}],[{"id":"2","num":16000},{"id":"110212","num":3},{"id":"114012","num":6}],[{"id":"2","num":40000},{"id":"110212","num":6},{"id":"114012","num":9}],[{"id":"2","num":80000},{"id":"110213","num":4},{"id":"114013","num":5}],[{"id":"2","num":160000},